<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="83137cfd-ea6a-490b-8692-d09bec479a0f"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="0eadc33b-8712-49ec-beaf-5b62095dcd73">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;172 (15d12 + 75)</p>
