<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="f7f8a0ba-d2ee-4958-89f6-224acaa30a24"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="751f7219-1299-42f7-8f2e-2c8b64e2fc89">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;207 (18d12 + 90)</p>
