<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="391c51d3-21d4-44f4-b969-af5a996e8f62">Huge dragon, chaotic evil</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="12ea7871-8f0c-49ed-af48-6b0b52dff07a"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="9f6e3aba-694e-4d10-81f3-b2e2758f3268">Armor Class</span>&nbsp;19 (natural armor)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="563db0d1-09c3-4746-a90e-8de34191a998"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="4fc0cadb-1103-4a6a-82ac-31310e4bd336">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;256 (19d12 + 133)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="2c28a19d-5dad-48ae-964b-dd5ea8612fa8"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="90a39069-d811-47d4-a56d-ca6f2d37ef2e">Speed</span>&nbsp;40 ft., climb 40 ft., fly 80 ft.</p>
