<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="0f472fe3-9f6c-4422-b236-c8758e7bad08"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="75e06061-a403-4271-ae35-f03351234e3e">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;297 (17d20 + 119)</p>
