<div class="stat-block-ability-scores-data" data-content-chunk-id="c0534109-d3c7-40c7-8a42-17b166a78951"><span class="stat-block-ability-scores-score" data-content-chunk-id="4ef9fc1b-fdd7-48c6-a8a9-5ed78ea0f975">21</span><span class="stat-block-ability-scores-modifier" data-content-chunk-id="b9bf7563-b032-4df2-a7ac-051eb5c9a895">(+5)</span></div>
