<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Title" data-content-chunk-id="913ed15d-cc34-4bde-bc13-b8029e553350"><a class="tooltip-hover monster-tooltip" href="/monsters/16780-ancient-gold-dragon" data-tooltip-href="/monsters/16780-tooltip">Ancient Gold Dragon</a></p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="33c53224-a880-4148-9f12-931be6b57507">Gargantuan dragon, lawful good</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="a3e771f7-0ae0-4e77-bf42-c621ca82c608"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="42ba26fe-ea80-40ce-85d9-1e2f714a7e46">Armor Class</span>&nbsp;22 (natural armor)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="7d201afd-e224-4760-8696-65a3e888265f"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="0498f34b-59df-483e-a8ef-2b7f34e99d27">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;546 (28d20 + 252)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="5ee9f781-280d-4031-bf4a-2f0c48a4f596"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="9334f8ed-baa5-423e-af2b-0a81173df151">Speed</span>&nbsp;40 ft., fly 80 ft., swim 40 ft.</p>
