<div class="stat-block-ability-scores-data" data-content-chunk-id="dd78599c-fe6c-43c1-a21d-ff44ae5e6270"><span class="stat-block-ability-scores-score" data-content-chunk-id="008832bd-2bd8-460b-8c54-88c4ecc8d53f">14</span><span class="stat-block-ability-scores-modifier" data-content-chunk-id="94216767-1b9a-47bb-af51-46c7c0b3d15f">(+2)</span></div>
