<div class="stat-block-ability-scores-data" data-content-chunk-id="555579f4-f133-4142-b73c-4c6050cf4945"><span class="stat-block-ability-scores-score" data-content-chunk-id="c7bd671b-eaa4-4c4c-b482-c6e05d440f71">18</span><span class="stat-block-ability-scores-modifier" data-content-chunk-id="b0cd33db-2280-407a-a66e-d8dbc2e989f5">(+4)</span></div>
