<div class="stat-block-ability-scores-data" data-content-chunk-id="ec2927b8-4924-4164-b702-cc9c7f6fef61"><span class="stat-block-ability-scores-score" data-content-chunk-id="82f1aac2-77ad-461e-a8ff-80025c201e75">17</span><span class="stat-block-ability-scores-modifier" data-content-chunk-id="aba0a568-9efe-4827-aedd-1c0535ebf9d4">(+3)</span></div>
