<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="a2375810-dcc8-4307-9031-8e213d4d2266">Gargantuan dragon, lawful evil</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="2b8d97b1-c4a4-4e04-8edd-bc50ecb8758b"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="87dc2d67-3b8f-4b7a-b462-d0c562259dfb">Armor Class</span>&nbsp;21 (natural armor)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="2c308c8f-6ce8-4b01-9066-97042e7f3969"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="8bb0d056-45c6-4c20-b611-48068710d045">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;385 (22d20 + 154)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="8850d820-c36f-47df-8496-e34ba552ea04"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="05184cc8-4d95-4074-a59c-240994866cca">Speed&nbsp;</span>40 ft., fly 80 ft., swim 40 ft.</p>
