<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="c63897d2-a62a-40d5-a117-d4f29469c11d"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="60def739-840e-4ca2-bc60-d2c63f3031ee">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;546 (28d20 + 252)</p>
