<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="7a9d6ca2-694b-4f31-ac66-543d604e6c38"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="e5e05e72-c153-4f03-9458-1faa53b4a903">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;33 (6d8 + 6)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="8f6fefb8-073f-4a84-b2e8-618fb7fadfce"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="4fe04887-0392-44e4-a716-f9e84b8aa533">Sp</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="aa31561e-3c66-4139-8877-b5915c63d037">eed</span>&nbsp;25 ft.</p>
