<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="92be00b9-b2fe-47b0-b4bb-b936b4384151"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="baa48f9a-97b9-4255-9428-9037a057dfd0">Challenge</span>&nbsp;0 (10 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body-Last--apply-before-heading-" data-content-chunk-id="971820af-b7a4-46d6-ae93-599983537482"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="7b4cb245-f0b7-490b-869f-99129c9daee5">False Appearance.</span>&nbsp;While the shrub remains motionless, it is indistinguishable from a normal shrub.</p>
